A
A=\begin{bmatrix} d & u^{T}\\  u & H  \end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix} \sqrt d & 0\\  \frac{u}{\sqrt d} & I_{n-1}  \end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix} 1 & 0\\  0 & K  \end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix} \sqrt d & \frac{u^{T}}{\sqrt{d}}\\  0 & I_{n-1}  \end{bmatrix}
K=H-\frac{1}{d}uu^{T}
K\in \mathbb{R}^{n-1,n-1}
P = \begin{bmatrix}\sqrt{d} & \frac{u^T}{\sqrt{d}}\\ 0 & I_{n-1}\end{bmatrix}
P^{-1} = \begin{bmatrix}\frac{1}{\sqrt{d}} & -\frac{u^T}{d}\\ 0 & I_{n-1} \end{bmatrix},
A = P^T \begin{bmatrix}1 & 0\\ 0 & K\end{bmatrix} P
\begin{bmatrix}1 & 0\\ 0 & K\end{bmatrix} = (P^T)^{-1} A P^{-1},
